Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:44.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:12.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:21.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:30.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:40.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:47.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:44.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:49.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.82,0:22:53.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:58.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:02.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.62,0:23:12.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:21.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:30.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:40.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.57,0:23:47.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:48.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.10,0:01:01.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:06.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:10.46,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:14.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:20.10,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.87,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:34.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.97,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:52.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:56.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:00.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:06.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:17.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:22.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
